    <div class="register container-fluid d-flex flex-row align-items-center justify-content-center p-0" >
        <div class="register-subcon col-xl-8 col-lg-10 col-md-11 col-10 row"> 
            <div style="max-height:90vh; overflow-y: scroll ;" class="c-div col-lg-8 col-12 d-flex flex-column justify-content-center border p-lg-5 p-md-4 p-sm-5 p-4 mx-auto">
                <div  id="data-notice" >
                    <h1>DATA PRIVACY NOTICE</h1>
                    <p class="mt-3">This Privacy Notice explains what information we collect, process, and share; why we do so; and your rights with regard to your information. </p>
                    <p><span>PERSONAL INFORMATION</span></p>
                    <p>We collect the following personal information from you when you sign up or create an account in relation to the Contactless Contact Tracing System.</p>
                   
                    <div class="col-10 mx-auto">
