                    <p>We adhere to the Data Privacy Act of 2012, the researchers commit to ensuring that all personal information obtained will be secured and remain confidential. And all collected personal data given will be used and utilized solely for academic purposes ONLY. The following information enables us to properly process the online registration for the system. The personal information shall not be shared or disclosed with other parties without consent unless the disclosure is required by, or in compliance with applicable laws and regulations. All information from the user will be automatically deleted after 30 days. </p>
                    <button id="initialSubmit" class="btn btn-grad col-12" type="submit">
                      Continue
                    </button>
                    <div class="col-12 d-flex justify-content-center" >
                        <a href="/" class="mx-auto mt-4">Go back to home page</a>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div  id="data-privacy" style="display: none;">
                    <h1>DATA PRIVACY NOTICE</h1>
                    <p class="mt-3">In accordance with the <span>Data Privacy Act (DPA) of 2012</span> and its Implementing Rules and Regulations (IRR), which became effective on September 9, 2016.</p>
